name: Building a web application with Mojolicious and Ember - Part Two
body: This is the second part of a multi-part tutorial which will help you get started developing web applications using [Mojolicious](http://mojolicious.org) and [Ember](http://emberjs.com). If you're looking for the [first part, here it is](http://keithbro.github.io/build-an-app-with-mojolicious-and-ember-part-1)
